## gstack skills

This project has gstack skills installed at `.agents/skills/`.
When the user mentions a slash-command, read the corresponding SKILL.md and follow it.

Available slash-commands:
- /office-hours — brainstorm and validate ideas (startup or builder mode)
- /plan-ceo-review — CEO/founder strategy review of a plan
- /plan-eng-review — engineering architecture review of a plan
- /plan-design-review — designer's eye review of a plan
- /autoplan — run all three reviews automatically
- /design-consultation — create a design system from scratch
- /review — pre-landing PR code review
- /ship — create PR with version bump and changelog
- /investigate — systematic root-cause debugging
- /qa — QA test a web app and fix bugs
- /qa-only — QA report without fixes
- /design-review — visual QA audit with fixes
- /codex — second opinion via OpenAI Codex CLI
- /cso — security audit (OWASP Top 10, STRIDE)
- /retro — weekly engineering retrospective
- /document-release — update docs after shipping
- /browse — headless browser for testing
- /benchmark — performance regression detection
- /canary — post-deploy monitoring
- /careful — safety guardrails for destructive commands
- /freeze — restrict edits to a directory
- /unfreeze — remove freeze restriction
- /guard — combine /careful + /freeze